INSTANT CARD APPLICATION FORM

To qualify for an instant card, you must be 18 years old or older, a resident of the Republic of Ghana.

INSTANT CARD APPLICATION FORM

Thank you for choosing the UBA card. Our customer service team will call you shortly to advise you on your nearest branch. Please visit the branch with a passport picture and any of these acceptable cards:

  • Driver’s license
  • SSNIT Biometric card
  • Voter’s ID
  • Passport
